i-periodic\nvariables. We identify examples of periodic accretors and extinction-driven\nperiodicity among them (with periods up to 5 yr) though more data are needed to\nclassify some cases. The data suggest that dynamic interactions with a\ncompanion may control the accretion rate in a substantial proportion of\neruptive systems, although star-disc interactions should also be considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Mar 2021 16:43:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 10:00:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
